  基于共性因子和多元回归对大学生手机使用情况与基础课和专业课成绩之间的相关性分析
  Analysis of the Correlation between College Students’ Mobile Phone Use and the Grades of Basic Courses and Specialized Courses Based on the Common Factor and Multiple Regression
 
